Interface Clearable

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AxisAngleBasics, GeometryObject<T>, Matrix3DBasics, Point2DBasics, Point3DBasics, QuaternionBasics, Tuple2DBasics, Tuple3DBasics, Tuple4DBasics, Vector2DBasics, Vector3DBasics, Vector4DBasics
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AffineTransform, AxisAngle, AxisAngle32, Matrix3D, Point2D, Point2D32, Point3D, Point3D32, Quaternion, Quaternion32, QuaternionBasedTransform, RigidBodyTransform, RotationMatrix, RotationScaleMatrix, Vector2D, Vector2D32, Vector3D, Vector3D32, Vector4D, Vector4D32

    public interface Clearable
    Interface used for geometry objects which data can be cleared by either resetting it with setToZero() or invalidating it with setToNaN().

    • Method Summary
